<div class="zm-item-rich-text expandable js-collapse-body" data-resourceid="16618830" data-action="/answer/content" data-author-name="马永新" data-entry-url="/question/60987107/answer/495289309">

<textarea hidden class="content">&lt;p&gt;动物摆拍，一些几乎把动物折腾到死来摆拍的黑镜头，胶水，钉子，绳子来固定动物的各种动作，无所不用其极。照片看似有趣，实则惨不忍睹。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a706a0dd336d8e7a3bdba8e75fad0e91_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;1005&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1143&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-034ebe601a4357d5fb24f63c6052ecef_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;1005&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a706a0dd336d8e7a3bdba8e75fad0e91_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;腿上的大块渗血显示它被外力扭伤过&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1c683417a624eb962e406954e3f3668b_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;582&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;297&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-676c62ca4bffaba2125cc172adec0ca8_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;582&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1c683417a624eb962e406954e3f3668b_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-2c39e8ea2b718c4f7a554f6b8b09afa4_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;978&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;725&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-bd65b3ca56cdbb5274c09101864a7652_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;978&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-2c39e8ea2b718c4f7a554f6b8b09afa4_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;两个都伤得惨不忍睹。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f231fcea118707bc9e01ff7a3b9235ee_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;260&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;156&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-adb2707e83e8f468c97dd1ef21fe2b27_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;260&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-e3b90c683d6e834b4afedf8732958ee2_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;220&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;325&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b305378e03233c3c07a39bb91cbd10a0_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;220&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-988086de60718ae360e562d17b784797_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;1067&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;667&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f5b610f0f3ba7a8eed602fc1866172ea_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;1067&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-988086de60718ae360e562d17b784797_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;半个身子都在慎血……&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-56877698cefd80f4c5629191a8310d79_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;222&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;237&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-b7a063d6ec3b7a4559e01f2158185009_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;222&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;林蛙被贴在树上动不了，然后在它身上贴各种动物。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-84a9f2446a007eeeef71553acc289a59_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;489&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1361&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-d44274c2e593307c2663c9075bb2c372_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;489&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-84a9f2446a007eeeef71553acc289a59_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;名叫Shikhei的印尼摄影师发布的青蛙竖中指照片，专家指出，树蛙不可能主动竖中指，它的肌肉不允许它这样做。摄影师“是用线来迫使动物摆成各种姿势，后期再ps掉。因为这类照片的动物抬起的肢体总会排在一条直线上。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-6a454e61a8b9a0e3a85fefcdfda349ce_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;1073&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1233&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-38dcebd47832af23093a05636ef4cf95_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;1073&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-6a454e61a8b9a0e3a85fefcdfda349ce_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-80324eee8eaa9a2ebe52f650740ea1e4_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;944&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;652&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-c03c0e2b0b705139f05f4a4ef2e8fc8c_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;944&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-80324eee8eaa9a2ebe52f650740ea1e4_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-66bb02bc45104db90aeeae1f2d2b2b56_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;939&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1088&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-b6c92b8076459e0d5dbfd12b03e00f21_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;939&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-66bb02bc45104db90aeeae1f2d2b2b56_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-94e733c6bd7207b9e940eeff2336c952_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;936&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;544&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-a544ac79e79f89784fe1cf98d8851b7e_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;936&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-94e733c6bd7207b9e940eeff2336c952_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-bcf37f293994432e4251b39222ddf73e_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;899&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1172&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-ba481b5aa1d7d474387dab83c3c0321b_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;899&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-bcf37f293994432e4251b39222ddf73e_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;用线固定各种姿态，后面再p掉&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-0baff348878cd3ffdd29e5188b5f3af2_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;940&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;636&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-83131591a16acdeaa97222a982b9e07e_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;940&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-0baff348878cd3ffdd29e5188b5f3af2_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-133ea2f0d4fbfd536bc17c86d582177d_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;853&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;529&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-69f409b90eebfb57e79151b67677c251_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;853&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-133ea2f0d4fbfd536bc17c86d582177d_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-640f3236ee04da6bc1b4672a5e057a1f_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;872&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;506&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-639824ed69b9c5517c0ede8e8cb7bfa7_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;872&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-640f3236ee04da6bc1b4672a5e057a1f_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-1f067fc921462adcea272a31aa773b35_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;910&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1266&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-137f1596c3419fa5ce3d5efa8acf2c1d_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;910&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-1f067fc921462adcea272a31aa773b35_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;以下这张作品，更是Shikhei Goh在国家地理杂志摄影比际大赛中拿过奖的。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-11bef9ad60aa13eab419faa5075165ad_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;930&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;667&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-9bb108f0759cb42292a7d576e732b065_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;930&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-11bef9ad60aa13eab419faa5075165ad_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;看同系列别的照片就会发现其实是把蜻蜓固定在枯枝上然后人为用水喷。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-27b7bcfd27a9b04b62b35a32a186bf78_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;945&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;644&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-f08b83cac03df341b6e2da20fb2e355a_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;945&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-27b7bcfd27a9b04b62b35a32a186bf78_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;还有摄影师Nicolas Reusens这张入选了2014索尼世界摄影大赛精彩的作品，也是摆拍。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-5b43124c9cdea865473815095c23853d_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;884&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;646&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-e6a83157f0108b13c25ad56cc7eec673_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;884&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-5b43124c9cdea865473815095c23853d_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;搜索一下他的其他照片，还有这样的……&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-fad4049dfce99515ef80bc8f80fbe8e6_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;881&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;569&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ba6af2a30642da54631106cd92d4151f_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;881&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-fad4049dfce99515ef80bc8f80fbe8e6_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;【一匹“野狼”从两棵桦树之间探出头】&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;真相却是，狼被铁链拴在后面那棵树上。饲养员就把生肉扔到狼的面前，诱导它钻进两棵树之间的缝隙……摄影师再在旁边趁机按下快门。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3718b6d7d97ab1c7995861389a6ebe5e_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;1068&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;585&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-d9b598fc43e2e463f4f8aa165504fb7e_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;1068&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3718b6d7d97ab1c7995861389a6ebe5e_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;《每日邮报》发布的这组“狼失其鹿，熊狼大战”图，鹿是人工摆放的死鹿，狼和熊也都是听从驯兽师的命令，故意“演”了一出“打戏”。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;然而，这组图却在不同的平台被转发了上万次。利益链条背后是它们的眼泪。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-753fcf992bf1652c014eb9195514011a_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;957&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;843&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-9a78899f243b402075ca419585f817a6_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;957&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-753fcf992bf1652c014eb9195514011a_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;在这些利益的背后，被圈养的是一个个可怜的动物。它们被迫配合人类摆出特定姿势，成为无良摄影师追名逐利的工具。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3dc282f171fa69c58e344e0ae8bb3fed_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;1071&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;682&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-e501e6713a97277548e3e7b4c5358012_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;1071&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3dc282f171fa69c58e344e0ae8bb3fed_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;摆拍生态摄影并不是新闻，把虫子钉在木头上等雀鸟吃、用胶水把雀鸟固定在树上拍照、又或是剪掉树枝好拍摄鸟巢，种种生态摄影所带来的是一张张令人惊讶的照片，​​及一次次可怕的生态灾难。让我们觉得逗趣的“萌照”背后，是以对动物的残忍虐待换来的。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-467b13aed4dd12c27aea5e17750443e0_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;928&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1176&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-561cc91674662ae669b02714aa77353e_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;928&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-467b13aed4dd12c27aea5e17750443e0_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2c9c9f477b052b1e809900806a554d20_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;1012&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1443&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-79c0ac97ec57d1671e2062b499cad1e1_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;1012&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2c9c9f477b052b1e809900806a554d20_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-732ddce1b9e8a46d02037a9fc512ec1e_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;882&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;574&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-7eca48bd58648248a0cfc8e59331a146_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;882&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-732ddce1b9e8a46d02037a9fc512ec1e_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-ad322cae81662139dde5caba53b6abe6_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;1059&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;729&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-488ff9fef60d127560938ae42f793559_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;1059&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-ad322cae81662139dde5caba53b6abe6_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-4d5ea85a7a3b0f316b7c0c46ec3a8bfd_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;1039&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;662&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-9455b4bbf0d5634b00c0f1b938b1eb93_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;1039&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-4d5ea85a7a3b0f316b7c0c46ec3a8bfd_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ab1c5d8daa9e7195abf7d2b90556f57c_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;937&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1170&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-4dcab7f4150942dd4a53496a6d54ff5c_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;937&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ab1c5d8daa9e7195abf7d2b90556f57c_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-8372f1b0a9a83a26ff2e156ea82dc3a8_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;1058&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;1147&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-8886780266888a8d6388f0b37941aa9d_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;1058&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-8372f1b0a9a83a26ff2e156ea82dc3a8_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;相关报道&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//fotomen.cn/2013/07/29/baipai-2/&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;伤不起的印尼摆拍摄影&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//m.sohu.com/a/203067270_661496&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;野生动物摆拍造假&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//sn.people.com.cn/n2/2017/0505/c186331-30137955.html&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;野生动物摄影居然是摆拍的&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//3g.163.com/news/article/CKDDMGPL0001875P.html%3Fclickfrom%3Dsogou_adapt&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;揭秘拍摄野生动物背后：饲养员指导动物摆造型，每个动物明码标价&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;所有文字资料与图片均来自于网络&lt;/p&gt;</textarea>


